              </section>
            </output>
          </browser-window>
          <figcaption class="pe-caption">One script adds keyboard navigation (<kbd>↑</kbd><kbd>↓</kbd> <kbd>Home</kbd> <kbd>End</kbd>), ARIA roles, command palette, and 30 interactive components.</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </details>
    </tab-set>

    <p class="pe-meta"><small>This section is itself a progressive enhancement demo — without JavaScript, <code>&lt;tab-set&gt;</code> degrades to a native exclusive accordion via the <code>name</code> attribute on <code>&lt;details&gt;</code>.</small></p>
